Client & Franchise Outcomes
Goal: Deliver Dockerfile Improvement Recommendations as a Service
By the end of Q2 2026, design, implement, and release Dockerfile Improvement Recommendations as a Service with possible extensions such as prompts via Workspaces, Aqua, or Assist, integration via VSaaS and other appropriate routes with production-ready APIs and documented consumption patterns.

Goal: Deliver Dockerfile Improvement Recommendations as a Service
By the end of Q2 2026, design, implement, and release image security Improvement Recommendations (CVEs, base image, root usage etc)  as a Service with possible extensions such as prompts via Workspaces, Aqua, or Assist, integration via VSaaS and other appropriate routes with production-ready APIs and documented consumption patterns.
